latestIgtvVideos.title: 🥰🥰 TLC For My Skin Twice a Week 🥰🥰
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
1. Apply an even layer of @thebodyshopindia Chinese Ginseng and Rice Clarifying Polishing Mask all over your face and neck.
2. Let it sit until try.
3. Wet your face a bit and gently scrub your face and neck. 
4. Apply the @Innisfreeindia My Real Squeeze Mask - Green Tea.
5. Apply the remaining essence on the neck and hands.
6. Do not wash.
7. Finish with The Body Shop Vitamin E Lip Balm.
P.S - Hair band 🐰 and the silicone brush (comes with a bowl and measuring spoons) from @mumusoindia
